Class EntityReturn

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.loader.plan.spi.AbstractPlanNode
      • org.hibernate.loader.plan.spi.AbstractFetchOwner
        • org.hibernate.loader.plan.spi.EntityReturn
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CopyableReturn, EntityReference, FetchOwner, IdentifierDescriptionInjectable, Return, ResultSetProcessingContext.EntityKeyResolutionContext

    public class EntityReturn
extends AbstractFetchOwner
implements Return, EntityReference, CopyableReturn
    Represents an entity return value in the query results. Not the same as a result (column) in the JDBC ResultSet!
